notes: JM Davison's highest score in ODIs (previous: 31 v Kenya at Cape Town, 2002/03)
I Maraj and JM Davison's partnership of 96 set a new Canadian 1st wicket partnership record in ODIs (previous: 54 CJD Chappell and GR Sealy v Pakistan at Leeds, 1979)
JM Davison score is the highest by a Canadian in ODIs (previous: 71 IS Billcliff v Kenya at Cape Town, 2002/03)
When JM Davison reached 76 (12.4 overs) he pasted the record for most runs for Canada in ODIs (previous: IS Billcliff 114 runs)
JM Davison and D Chumney's partnership of 60 set a new Canadian 2nd wicket partnership record in ODIs (previous: 31 GR Sealy and FA Dennis v Pakistan at Leeds, 1979)
Canada's total is the highest team total for Canada in all ODIs (previous: 197 v kenya at Cape Town, 2002/03)
VC Drakes' best bowling in World Cups (previous: 2/33 v South Africa at Cape Town, 2002/03)
VC Drakes' best bowling in ODIs (previous: 4/18 v Bangladesh at Dhaka, 2002/03)
Man of the Match: JM Davison

milestones.description: John Davison and Ishwar Maraj's 95-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 54 between Chappell and Glenroy Sealy
Chumney and John Davison's 59-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between Glenroy Sealy and Dennis
John Davison has broken the record for most sixes (8) in ODIs for CAN, going past Ian Billcliff's 2
John Davison has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (68) in an innings in ODIs for CAN, going past Ian Billcliff's 44
John Davison has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for CAN, going past Ian Billcliff's 2
Joe Harris has broken the record for most ODIs (4) as captain for CAN, going past Mauricette
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for CAN, going past Ian Billcliff
John Davison and Ishwar Maraj's 95-run partnership is CAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 86 between Joe Harris and Ian Billcliff
John Davison's 111 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for CAN), surpassing Ian Billcliff's 71
John Davison has become the top scorer for CAN in ODIs with 150 runs, going past Ian Billcliff's 114
